<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title><%= title %></title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/header') %>
    <main>
        <section class="careers-hero-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h1>Careers at Nageshwaram Foundation Trust</h1>
                <p>Join our dedicated team and contribute to shaping the future of education in rural India.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="careers-intro-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Build a Rewarding Career with Impact</h2>
                <p>At Nageshwaram Foundation Trust, we believe that our greatest asset is our people. We are a growing organization committed to making a tangible difference in the lives of students and communities. If you are passionate about education, driven by a desire to serve, and eager to work in a dynamic and supportive environment, we invite you to explore career opportunities with us.</p>
                <p>We offer a collaborative culture where your contributions are valued, and your professional growth is encouraged. Whether you are an experienced educator, an administrative professional, or a support staff member, your skills can help us further our mission.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="opportunities-section">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>What We Look For</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>**Passion for Education:** A genuine commitment to fostering learning and holistic development.</li>
                    <li>**Dedication:** A strong work ethic and a desire to make a positive impact.</li>
                    <li>**Team Player:** Ability to collaborate effectively with colleagues, students, and parents.</li>
                    <li>**Innovation:** Openness to new ideas and modern pedagogical approaches.</li>
                    <li>**Integrity:** Adherence to high ethical standards and professional conduct.</li>
                </ul>

                <h2>Current Openings</h2>
                <p>We frequently have openings in various roles, including:</p>
                <ul>
                    <li>Teaching positions (various subjects and levels) at N.R.K. Public School</li>
                    <li>Administrative staff</li>
                    <li>Counselors</li>
                    <li>Support staff (librarians, lab assistants, etc.)</li>
                </ul>
                <p>Even if you don't see a specific opening listed, we are always keen to hear from talented individuals who share our vision. Please feel free to send us your resume.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="call-to-action">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Apply Today</h2>
                <p>Take the first step towards a fulfilling career where you can inspire change and shape futures.</p>
                <a href="/contact" class="cta-button primary">Send Your Resume / Inquire</a>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <%- include('../partials/footer') %>
</body>
</html>
